{"tid":2341713,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Homebake走高檔 人流多","createTime":"2020-12-26T14:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T05:55:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b285939c647435f45acfc565f0b4739c2ad991","tid":2341713,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201224/MB7NDGVUWZA3BJKXQBFAVEJM6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201224%2FMB7NDGVUWZA3BJKXQBFAVEJM6I%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=f6993004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201224%2FMB7NDGVUWZA3BJKXQBFAVEJM6I%2F&h=10c08ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201224/MB7NDGVUWZA3BJKXQBFAVEJM6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nHomebake走高檔 人流多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/we4LYO9NclmBYc93plGHqnxUXQw=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SCYDAZ7S7BEARJWUPIZVBA2S5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwe4LYO9NclmBYc93plGHqnxUXQw%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSCYDAZ7S7BEARJWUPIZVBA2S5A.jpg&h=98f1833f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■麵包店Homebake為美心集團旗下新品牌，不少人不知就裏幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】除了網上商店及外賣平台，美心集團今年亦有零星拓展新實體品牌。本報記者昨到訪美心於上月開業、位於中環萬邦行的麵包店Homebake，此店同樣未見顯示於官網；現場所見，裝修格調完全不同於「美心西餅」，店內人流絡繹不絕，門外更不時出現長長人龍，有光顧者不知道此店背後來頭。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藍店疫市變陣求生 新增7餐飲商標  美心攻「偽獨立」品牌<br />\n<br />\nHomebake走高檔路線，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「獨立」品牌fb極少讚好<br />\n<br />\n雖然美心未有公開披露新開設的多個品牌，但「獨立」品牌要成功打響名堂仍有一段漫長道路。年初登記商標的兩個外賣平台：便當日子Bento Days及CHICK IN A BOX，食正外賣潮流卻未成功爭取高度關注；截至昨日，兩個facebook專頁的「讚好（like）」僅為22個及182個，設有實體店的Homebake亦只有676個讚好。"},{"pid":"62e265cb2f5d5a333ef17a07ab818de644dcd0ed","tid":2341713,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e42acc124f8421c6aaba97572349d693555e87","tid":2341713,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"下欄嘢 當上菜賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}